1. *Nedostaješ* mi svaki dan. (I miss you every day.)
2. Osećam da mi *nedostaješ*. (I feel like I'm missing you.)
3. Svi ti *nedostaju* tvoji prijatelji. (All your friends miss you.)
4. Kada si otišao, *nedostajao* si mi. (When you left, I was missing you.)
5. *Nedostaješ* nam na večeri. (You are missing from dinner.)